---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Your Story"
  description="Hear, Speak, Do, Live — how Harbor City Church walks with Jesus together, and for the long haul."
  brand="main"
>

  <!-- ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="dc-hero">
    <div class="dc-hero__inner reveal">
      <p class="dc-eyebrow">Your Story &mdash;</p>
      <h1 class="dc-headline">
        Hear, Speak,<br />Do, Live<sup class="dc-tm">&trade;</sup>
      </h1>
      <p class="dc-sub">
        Your story, reshaped by his.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── THE FOUR VERBS ──────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="dc-verbs">
    <div class="dc-inner">

      <div class="dc-verb reveal">
        <span class="dc-verb__num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <div class="dc-verb__content">
          <h2 class="dc-verb__title">Hear the Word</h2>
          <p class="dc-verb__scripture">
            &ldquo;Faith comes by hearing.&rdquo; &mdash; Romans 10:17
          </p>
          <p class="dc-verb__body">
            Every transformed life begins with an open ear. We hear the Word
            preached on Sundays. We hear it read in quiet. We hear it spoken
            by the Spirit. The ear is the beginning.
          </p>
          <p class="dc-verb__body">
            At Harbor City Church, that&rsquo;s Sunday services, our sermon
            archive, and the daily practice of opening Scripture on your own.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dc-verb-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="dc-verb reveal">
        <span class="dc-verb__num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <div class="dc-verb__content">
          <h2 class="dc-verb__title">Speak the Word</h2>
          <p class="dc-verb__scripture">
            &ldquo;Let the redeemed of the Lord say so.&rdquo; &mdash; Psalm 107:2
          </p>
          <p class="dc-verb__body">
            What you hear gets woven into who you are when you start to speak
            it. Confession. Testimony. Prayer. Shared Scripture in small
            groups. When your tongue agrees with Heaven, something shifts in you.
          </p>
          <p class="dc-verb__body">
            At Harbor City Church, that&rsquo;s Groups, prayer ministry, and the
            ordinary courage of telling someone what God has done.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dc-verb-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="dc-verb reveal">
        <span class="dc-verb__num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <div class="dc-verb__content">
          <h2 class="dc-verb__title">Do the Word</h2>
          <p class="dc-verb__scripture">
            &ldquo;Be doers of the word, and not hearers only.&rdquo; &mdash; James 1:22
          </p>
          <p class="dc-verb__body">
            Hearing without doing is self-deception. Faith takes shape in
            action &mdash; serving, giving, showing up for someone else&rsquo;s
            struggle, obeying the quiet nudge of the Spirit.
          </p>
          <p class="dc-verb__body">
            At Harbor City Church, that&rsquo;s Dream Team, Growth Track,
            outreach, and the daily obedience of answering what God has asked
            of you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dc-verb-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="dc-verb reveal">
        <span class="dc-verb__num" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
        <div class="dc-verb__content">
          <h2 class="dc-verb__title">Live the Word</h2>
          <p class="dc-verb__scripture">
            &ldquo;It is no longer I who live, but Christ who lives in me.&rdquo;
            &mdash; Galatians 2:20
          </p>
          <p class="dc-verb__body">
            The first three verbs done consistently over time produce a fourth
            thing &mdash; a life. Not a program completed. Not a course
            graduated. A life transformed. You stop doing the Word as a project
            and start living as the Word&rsquo;s person.
          </p>
          <p class="dc-verb__body">
            This is the long arc of Harbor City discipleship. It takes years.
            It&rsquo;s worth it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── STEPS AND WAVES ────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="dc-waves">
    <div class="dc-waves__inner reveal">
      <h2 class="dc-waves__headline">Steps, and waves.</h2>
      <p class="dc-waves__body">
        Discipleship has a shape. It&rsquo;s sequential &mdash; hearing builds
        into speaking, speaking into doing, doing into a transformed life.
        That&rsquo;s the step part.
      </p>
      <p class="dc-waves__body">
        But it&rsquo;s also a spiral. You walk the whole thing in a year, and
        it changes you. Then you walk it again &mdash; and it changes you more,
        because the you who&rsquo;s walking it the second time isn&rsquo;t who
        you were the first time. That&rsquo;s the wave part.
      </p>
      <p class="dc-waves__body">
        Steps give discipleship structure. Waves give it depth. A year of Hear,
        Speak, Do produces a new way to Live. A lifetime of them produces a saint.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── GIVE US ONE YEAR ──────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="dc-year">
    <div class="dc-year__inner reveal">
      <p class="dc-year__eyebrow">The Invitation &mdash;</p>
      <h2 class="dc-year__headline">Give us one year of your life.</h2>
      <p class="dc-year__body">
        Come out to the church and give us one year of your life.
      </p>
      <p class="dc-year__body">
        One year in which you hear the word, you speak the word, and you do the
        word. One year in which you live the word of God.
      </p>
      <p class="dc-year__body">
        And we guarantee your life will never be the same again.
      </p>
      <a href="/nextsteps" class="dc-year__cta">I&rsquo;m in</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── EVERY SEASON ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="dc-seasons">
    <div class="dc-inner">
      <div class="dc-seasons__inner reveal">
        <p class="dc-label">For Every Stage</p>
        <h2 class="dc-section-title">Every season belongs.</h2>
        <p class="dc-section-body">
          Every life has a rhythm. Single life. Married life. Raising kids.
          Empty-nester life. The slower rhythms of retirement. They don&rsquo;t
          all look the same, and discipleship doesn&rsquo;t pretend they do.
        </p>
        <p class="dc-section-body">
          What stays the same across every season is the process &mdash; Hear,
          Speak, Do, Live. How that shows up in your week will look different at
          25 than at 65. Both are legitimate. Both are growing. Both are
          Harbor City Church.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── CLOSE ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="dc-close">
    <div class="dc-inner">
      <div class="dc-close__inner reveal">
        <h2 class="dc-close__headline">Ready to take a step?</h2>
        <p class="dc-close__sub">Start with Growth Track &mdash; or just come on a Sunday.</p>
        <div class="dc-close__actions">
          <a href="/nextsteps" class="dc-btn dc-btn--gold">Plan your visit</a>
          <a href="/groups" class="dc-btn dc-btn--ghost">Find a group</a>
        </div>
        <p class="dc-close__note">
          Already walking with us? Join a Growth Track class or serve on the
          Dream Team.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── TRADEMARK ──────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="dc-trademark">
    <div class="dc-inner">
      <p>
        Hear, Speak, Do, Live is a discipleship framework of Harbor City Church.
        &copy; Harbor City Church, Baltimore.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ─── Layout ─── */
  .dc-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px;
  }

  /* ─── Shared label ─── */
  .dc-label {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--hcc-gold);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .dc-section-title {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    color: var(--hcc-midnight);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .dc-section-body {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
    color: var(--hcc-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 620px;
  }

  /* ─── Buttons ─── */
  .dc-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 14px 40px;
    transition: all var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .dc-btn--gold {
    background: var(--hcc-gold);
    color: var(--hcc-midnight);
  }

  .dc-btn--gold:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .dc-btn--ghost {
    border: 1px solid var(--hcc-midnight);
    color: var(--hcc-midnight);
  }

  .dc-btn--ghost:hover {
    background: var(--hcc-midnight);
    color: var(--hcc-white);
  }

  /* ─── Hero ─── */
  .dc-hero {
    background-color: var(--hcc-midnight);
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(14,27,46,0.55) 0%, rgba(14,27,46,0.72) 100%),
      url('/images/heroes/your-story.webp');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    padding: 200px 48px 160px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .dc-hero__inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .dc-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--hcc-gold);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .dc-headline {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(52px, 11vw, 128px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--hcc-white);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .dc-tm {
    font-size: 0.35em;
    vertical-align: super;
    line-height: 0;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .dc-sub {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ─── Four Verbs ─── */
  .dc-verbs {
    background: var(--hcc-cream);
    padding: 120px 0;
  }

  .dc-verb {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
    gap: 0 48px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 64px 0;
  }

  .dc-verb__num {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(64px, 8vw, 96px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--hcc-gold);
    line-height: 1;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  .dc-verb__title {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--hcc-midnight);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }

  .dc-verb__scripture {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--hcc-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }

  .dc-verb__body {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
    color: var(--hcc-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .dc-verb-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(14, 27, 46, 0.08);
  }

  /* ─── Steps and Waves ─── */
  .dc-waves {
    background: var(--hcc-midnight);
    padding: 120px 48px;
  }

  .dc-waves__inner {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .dc-waves__headline {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 60px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    color: var(--hcc-white);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .dc-waves__body {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* ─── Give Us One Year ─── */
  .dc-year {
    background: var(--hcc-gold);
    padding: 120px 48px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .dc-year__inner {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .dc-year__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--hcc-midnight);
    opacity: 0.55;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .dc-year__headline {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5.5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--hcc-midnight);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .dc-year__body {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
    color: var(--hcc-midnight);
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .dc-year__body + .dc-year__cta {
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .dc-year__cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--hcc-white);
    background: var(--hcc-midnight);
    padding: 14px 40px;
    transition: opacity var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .dc-year__cta:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* ─── Every Season ─── */
  .dc-seasons {
    background: var(--hcc-cream);
    padding: 120px 0;
  }

  .dc-seasons__inner {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  /* ─── Close ─── */
  .dc-close {
    background: var(--hcc-cream);
    padding: 0 0 120px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(14, 27, 46, 0.08);
  }

  .dc-close__inner {
    max-width: 680px;
    padding-top: 80px;
  }

  .dc-close__headline {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    color: var(--hcc-midnight);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .dc-close__sub {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--hcc-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .dc-close__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .dc-close__note {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--hcc-text-light);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* ─── Trademark footer ─── */
  .dc-trademark {
    background: var(--hcc-cream);
    padding: 0 0 64px;
  }

  .dc-trademark p {
    font-family: var(--hcc-font-sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--hcc-warm-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(14, 27, 46, 0.06);
    padding-top: 24px;
  }

  /* ─── Responsive ─── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .dc-hero {
      padding: 160px 24px 120px;
    }
    .dc-inner {
      padding: 0 24px;
    }
    .dc-verbs {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    .dc-verb {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 48px 0;
    }
    .dc-verb__num {
      font-size: 48px;
    }
    .dc-waves,
    .dc-year {
      padding: 80px 24px;
    }
    .dc-seasons {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
  }
</style>
